snippet.title: TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES II: The Secret of the Ooze Official Re-Release Trailer (2026)
snippet.description:
Official Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze Movie 35th Anniversary Re-Release 4K Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Brian Tochi Movie Trailer | Re-Release: 13 Mar 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/movie/xm7/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-the-secret-of-the-ooze-1991?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
The Turtles and the Shredder battle once again, this time for the last cannister of the ooze that created the Turtles, which Shredder wants to create an army of new mutants.

Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze (1991) is the action movie by Michael Pressman, starring Brian Tochi, Laurie Faso and Robbie Rist.
